------------------------------------------ HW 0 To-Do App ------------------------------------------

Overview: 

This is a to do web-app developed with HTML, JAVA, CSS.

Functionality:

The app allows the user to add tasks to a to do list. Users can edit or delete a a task 
on the list as well.

Files:

The folder contains three files:

1. index.HTML - defines the structure of the to do App
2. main.CSS - describes the presentation/formatting of the elements of the webapp
3. main.js - defines the underlying logic for interacting with various elements - 
add new task, edit task, delete task

How to run?

The web-app is locally run. To run the to-do list webapp simply select the index.html file and
either drag/drop onto a browser (Internet Explorer, Safari, Google Chrome, Firefox, Opera support
HTML). Alternatively navigate to the folder/directory where the files have been saved, right click 
on the index.html file and open with one of the aformentioned browsers.


